text.section:
"Agency on aging" means:
an area agency on aging;
the Dorchester County Commission on Aging, Inc.;
the Somerset County Commission on Aging, Inc.;
the Washington County Commission on Aging, Inc.; and
the Worcester County Commission on Aging, Inc.

section.section:
"Legislative body" includes:
a board of county commissioners;
a county council;
the legislative body of a municipal corporation;
for a community action agency, a governing body as defined in § 8-101 of the Housing and Community Development Article;
for an agency on aging:
the legislative body of the county that the agency on aging represents; or
for an area agency on aging that represents more than one county, the legislative body of each of the counties included in the jurisdiction of the area agency on aging;
for the University of Maryland Medical System Corporation, the Board of Directors of the corporation; and
for the Garrett County Office for Children, Youth and Families, the Board of County Commissioners for Garrett County.
